Class DkStrategyListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qtplaf.library.trading.server.servers.dukascopy.listeners.DkStrategyListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.dukascopy.api.IJFRunnable<com.dukascopy.api.IContext>, com.dukascopy.api.IStrategy

    public class DkStrategyListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.dukascopy.api.IStrategy
    Dukascopy strategy implementation to listen to strategy events, to retrieve the context, the history, ticks and all data that requires a running strategy.
    Author:
    Miquel Sas
